translation.Name: Buak_Note_00
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Little? Too little?! I was too little, he said- when I’m not even comparable to a mouse! What on Earth does dear baba know! To a mouse…I’m big. To a rat, even bigger! I can be big, baba! I can be a big man! I’m starting a band and moving to Canada with mama- and there’s nothing you can do about it!
